(e^{At}−I)/t\to A
t\to 0
\|(e^{At}−I)/t−A\|\to 0
t\to 0
A\in C^{n×n}
\|A^k\|\leq n^{k−1}\|A\|^k
e^{At}=I+At+{(At)^2}/2!+...+{(At)^k}/k!\\ e^{At}-I=At+{(At)^2}/2!+...+{(At)^k}/k!\\ (e^{At}-I)/t=A+{A^2t}/2!+...+{A^kt^{k-1}}/k!\\ \|(e^{At}−I)/t−A\|={A^2t}/2!+...+{A^kt^{k-1}}/k!
t→0
\|(e^{At}−I)/t−A\|\to 0
t\to 0
